high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the tub, then hang a right and walk up to the green bin.
Pick up the bar of soap off of the toilet tank to your right.
Walk over to the sink.
Put the bar of soap in the sink and turn on the water, after a couple of seconds turn off the water and remove the now clean bar of soap.
Turn right and walk over to the toilet.
Put the clean bar of soap on top of the toilet tank.
tasks.task_desc: Put a clean bar of soap on the toilet tank.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the small empty space between the toilet and the sink.
Pick up the bar of soap on the back of the toilet, behind the roll of toilet paper.
Move to the sink to your left.
Place the bar of soap in the sink, turn the water on, clean the sink out, turn the water off, and remove the bar of soap from the sink.
Move to your right, back to the toilet.
Place the bar of soap on the back of the toilet, between the candle and the pump bottle all the way to the right.
tasks.task_desc: Place a wet bar of soap on the back of the toilet.

high_descs: turn around to the toilet
pick up a soap bar
turn left to the sink
wet the soap with water
turn right and head to the toilet
place the soap on the toilet
tasks.task_desc: place a wet soap on the toilet
